<h1>Subscription Cancelled</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @customer.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Your subscription to <strong><%= @item.name %></strong> has been cancelled as of <%= @customer_subscription.cancelled_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>.</p>

<% if @customer_subscription.cancellation_reason.present? %>
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @customer_subscription.cancellation_reason %></p>
<% end %>

<h2>What this means:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>You will not be charged for future billing cycles</li>
  <li>Your access will continue until your current billing period ends</li>
  <li>You can reactivate your subscription anytime</li>
</ul>

<p>If you'd like to reactivate your subscription or have any questions, please contact us.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= client_subscriptions_url(subdomain: @business.subdomain) %>">View your subscriptions</a>
</p>

<p>Thank you for being a valued customer.</p> 